product.name: Yeezy Slides 'Onyx'
product.story_html: The adidas Yeezy Slide ‘Onyx’ brings a stealthy monochrome finish to Kanye West’s futuristic sandal. A single piece of injected EVA foam is molded for a comfortable fit. The minimalist design is highlighted by ventilated open-toe construction and a soft footbed marked with debossed adidas branding. The serrated outsole features strategic groove placement, good for a combination of impact protection, exceptional grip, and improved impact protection.

product.story: The Kool-Aid x Nike Ja 2 'Ohhh Yeah!' showcases mismatched color blocking, with a blue-to-black gradient design on the left shoe that nods to Blue Raspberry Kool-Aid. The right shoe channels the Cherry Red flavor with an upper that transitions from crimson to orange. A graphic atop the tongue depicts the Kool-Aid man crashing through a wall, while the character's 'Ohhh Yeah!' tagline is embroidered on the interior side. Heel tabs display Ja's '12:AM' branding in the classic Kool-Aid font. Black speckles coat the white Phylon midsole, supported underfoot by a glow-in-the-dark rubber outsole.

Jordan 1 Retro High OG Shattered Backboard (2025)
product.story: The 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shattered Backboard' revives the popular 2015 colorway, inspired by the jersey that Michael Jordan wore during an exhibition game in Italy following his rookie NBA season. (He shattered the backboard while executing a one-handed dunk.) The high-top sports a leather upper that combines white quarter panels with a black forefoot overlay and matching black Swoosh while orange accents land on the toe box, heel, and collar flap.

Nike SB Dunk Low CSEF
product.story: The CSEF x Nike Dunk Low SB 'White Clear Emerald' celebrates the intersection of higher education and skateboarding culture. Representing Nike's first collaboration with the College Skateboarding Educational Foundation, the low-top sports a Summit White leather upper with contrasting black accents on the suede toe box, patent leather Swoosh, and padded tongue. Grey suede wraps the low-cut collar, which is lined in emerald green mesh. Yellow leather back tabs display mismatched Nike and CSEF branding. A scantron-inspired tag adorns the tongue, while a graphic depicting CSEF's mascot graces the lateral heel.

product.story: The adidas Dame X 'Black Iron Metallic' presents one of the launch colorways of Damian Lillard's tenth signature shoe. Wavy TPU overlays in grey encircle the blacked-out upper, crafted from a combination of breathable mesh and padded textile. Lillard's personal logo adorns the tongue in royal blue, matching the adidas branding hit that decorates the heel tab. The sneaker is mounted on a matching black Lightstrike midsole.

product.name: H-Street OG 'Fizzy Green'
product.story: The PUMA H-Street OG 'Fizzy Green' delivers a vibrant colorway of a lifestyle model inspired by a late '90s track spike, the iconic PUMA Harambee. The bright green mesh upper is accented with synthetic leather overlays in metallic silver. Branding elements include a silver Fomstrip outlined in black embroidery, as well as PUMA's jumping cat logo at the tongue and heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via an EVA midsole, rendered in a wedge shape with a lightly flared heel.

product.name: Wmns H-Street OG 'Fizzy Green'
product.story: The PUMA Women's H-Street OG 'Fizzy Green' revives an early 2000s lifestyle runner inspired by an iconic track spike, the PUMA Harambee. Constructed from bright green mesh, the upper features synthetic leather overlays at the forefoot and heel in a shiny metallic silver finish. Additional silver accents land on the eyestay and Formstrip, the latter featuring wavy lines outlined in black embroidery. Underfoot, a grippy rubber outsole wraps up the low-profile EVA midsole.

product.name: Wmns H-Street OG 'Frosted Ivory Silver'
product.story: The PUMA Women's H-Street OG 'Frosted Ivory Silver' delivers a lightweight lifestyle runner that bridges the gap between streetwear and track and field. Built with light tan mesh, the streamlined upper features a metallic silver Formstrip outlined in black embroidery. Matching synthetic leather overlays in metallic silver reinforce the forefoot and heel. The sneaker rests on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported by a grippy rubber outsole that wraps up the toe.

product.name: H-Street OG 'Frosted Ivory Silver'
product.story: The PUMA H-Street OG 'Frosted Ivory Silver' revives an archival 2000s lifestyle runner inspired by the iconic PUMA Harambee track spike. The low-profile upper is crafted from light tan mesh with synthetic leather accents in metallic silver. They land on the eyestay, forefoot and heel overlay, and signature Formstrip. The lightweight upper is mounted on an EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a grippy black rubber outsole.

product.name: H-Street OG 'Black Silver'
product.story: The PUMA H-Street OG 'Black Silver' merges sprinting heritage with street-ready style, featuring a sleek black mesh upper with synthetic leather overlays in metallic silver. Outlined in black embroidery, the signature Formstrip is similarly rendered in a metallic silver finish. A molded footbed works in tandem with a lightweight EVA midsole to deliver a comfortable ride. The rubber outsole utilizes rounded lugs for durable traction.

product.name: Kobe Bryant x Air Force 1 Low Protro 'Mamba Mentality'
product.story: The Kobe Bryant x Nike Air Force 1 Low Protro 'Mamba Mentality' features a pale yellow leather upper, secured with wide patterned laces and accented with contrasting hints of purple along the edges. An oversized '8' — Kobe Bryant's first jersey number with the LA Lakers — is appliqued on the back heel, while the athlete's sheath logo appears on the purple woven tongue tag. This Protro edition of the AF1 packs a drop-in ReactX foam insole for responsive cushioning. The sneaker is mounted on a durable cupsole, highlighted by Kobe's signature on the lateral sidewall.

product.name: Jordan 11 Retro Low Bred (TD)
product.story: The 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 11 Retro Low TD 'Bred' revives a PE colorway that Michael Jordan wore during the 1996 NBA playoffs. Like the original, the low-top features a black ballistic mesh upper with a tonal patent leather mudguard. Jumpman branding in Varsity Red embellishes the tongue and back heel. A white foam midsole provides lightweight cushioning, while a red translucent rubber outsole yields durable traction for little feet.

product.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro TD 'Grape' 2025
product.story: The 2025 reissue of the Air Jordan 5 Retro TD 'Grape' brings back an original 1990 release, with a white leather upper featuring quarter panel netting and Nike Air branding on the back heel. Violet accents land on the tongue, contrasted by a turquoise Jumpman logo, and full-length foam midsole. The latter is adorned with signature shark tooth detailing in a bright teal hue.

product.name: Jalen Williams x Harden Vol. 9 'White Lucid Lime Pink'
Air Jordan 5 Retro PS 'Grape' 2025
product.story: Scaled down for little kids, the 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 5 Retro PS 'Grape' features a white leather upper with heritage details that include quarter panel netting and Nike Air branding on the heel. Atop the purple-hued tongue, a Jumpman logo stands out in turquoise embroidery. The sneaker rests on a violet foam midsole, accented with turquoise shark tooth detailing and supported by a translucent herringbone-traction outsole.

product.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro GS 'Grape' 2025
product.story: The 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 5 Retro GS 'Grape' brings back an OG colorway in kids sizing. Built with smooth white leather, the upper features quarter panel netting and molded TPU eyelets. A teal embroidered Jumpman adorns the purple-hued tongue, while Nike Air branding appears on the back heel. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a violet polyurethane midsole with turquoise shark tooth detailing and a visible Air-sole unit in the heel.

product.name: Jordan 11 Retro Low Bred (PS)
product.story: Made for little kids, the 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 11 Retro Low PS 'Bred' brings back an OG colorway of the legacy silhouette in low-top form. The sleek design features a black ballistic mesh upper with a tonal patent leather mudguard. An embroidered Jumpman logo in Varsity Red adorns the tongue, while a stylized '23' appears on the back tab. A crisp white foam midsole is supported underfoot by a red translucent rubber outsole.

product.name: Jordan 5 Retro Grape (2025)
product.story: The 2025 edition of the Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Grape' revives an OG colorway of the legacy silhouette. True to the 1990 release, Tinker Hatfield's classic design features a white leather upper with ventilated quarter panel netting and molded TPU eyelets. Atop the tongue, a teal embroidered Jumpman stands out against a purple backdrop. Nike Air branding decorates the back heel. The sneaker rests on a violet polyurethane midsole with turquoise shark tooth detailing and a visible Air-sole unit in the heel. A translucent rubber outsole provides durable traction underfoot.

MB.04 Lo 'Ice White'
product.story: The PUMA MB.04 Lo 'Ice White' delivers a squiggly texture on the off-white woven mesh upper, featuring an embroidered PUMA Formstrip. Melo's '1 of 1' branding adorns the tongue, while his wings logo graces the molded heel panel. A matching white NITROFOAM midsole provides lightweight cushioning with every step. Underfoot, a high-abrasion rubber outsole reveals Melo's 'Not From Here' tagline.

product.name: Teddy Santis x 991v2 Made in England 'Celestial Blue'
product.story: The Teddy Santis x New Balance 991v2 Made in England 'Celestial Blue' brings a hairy texture to the suede upper, rendered in a pastel blue finish with a color-matched mesh underlay. Tying into New Balance heritage, neutral grey accents make their way to the New Balance tongue tag, synthetic leather forefoot overlay, and back tab. The lifestyle runner sits atop a tow-tone ENCAP midsole, featuring FuelCell foam cushioning and semi-translucent ABZORB SBS pods in the forefoot and heel.

product.name: Teddy Santis x 991v2 Made in England 'Mineral Green'
Jordan 1 Retro Low OG Washed Teal (Women's)
product.story: The Women's Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG 'Washed Teal' is dressed in a suede upper in a faded turquoise hue. Hairy tonal suede is deployed on the signature Swoosh. A woven Nike Air tag decorates the tongue, while a printed Wings logo graces the back tab. Anchoring the sneaker is a mint green midsole, supported underfoot by a translucent rubber outsole.

product.name: Air Max Waffle Racer SP 'Bright Ceramic'
Air Max Waffle Racer SP 'Electrolime Flash Crimson'
ABZORB 2000 'Still Water'
product.story: The New Balance ABZORB 2000 'Still Water' delivers a tonal pastel colorway of the lifestyle running shoe, featuring a streamlined upper that merges breathable mesh with no-sew synthetic overlays. The signature 'N' logo is limited to the lateral side panel, while NB branding decorates the tongue tag. The powder blue hues continue on a full-length ABZORB midsole with SBS cushioning. Underfoot, a segmented rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

product.name: Nike Air Foamposite One Triple White
product.story: The Nike Air Foamposite One 'Triple White' brings a stark white Foamposite upper, featuring tonal leather construction on the eyestay and collar. Penny Hardaway's 1 Cent logo adorns the back tab and tongue in black. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a concealed foam midsole, augmented with a full-length Zoom Air unit and a second Zoom Air bag in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features an exposed carbon fiber shank plate in a black-and-white checkerboard pattern.

Better Gift Shop x Air Max DN8 'Revenge'
product.story: The Better Gift Shop x Nike Air Max Dn8 delivers a grey mesh upper with tonal no-sew overlays and reflective wave patterns inspired by traditional Japanese artwork. A molded blue mini-Swoosh adorns the lateral collar, while a lenticular tongue tag displays dual branding. The sneaker rests on a two-tone Phylon midsole that packs a pair of dual-pressured Air units, each housing four exposed tubes.

product.name: Wmns Pegasus Premium 'Summit White Bright Crimson'
product.story: The Nike Women's Pegasus Premium 'Summit White Bright Crimson' showcases a triple-stack of Nike's foremost cushioning technologies. The performance runner rides atop a responsive ZoomX foam midsole, augmented with a full-length Zoom Air unit that's tinted red and contoured to the natural profile of the foot. A layer of ReactX foam under the heel completes the performance features. Up top, a seamless build in stretchy white Flyknit features reflective accents and the Dynamic Midfoot System for a lockdown fit.

A Ma Maniére x Air Jordan 5 Retro OG 'Violet Ore'
product.story: The A Ma Maniere x Air Jordan 5 'Violet Ore' features a white leather upper with pre-yellowed quarter panel netting and an embroidered '23' on the lateral heel. Quilted textile in a rich burgundy hue lines the interior, matching the Nike Air heel logo and tongue. The reflective tongue displays Jumpman branding on the right shoe and A Ma Maniere's 'A' logo on the left. An additional splash of burgundy lands on the polyurethane midsole, accented with tonal shark tooth detailing and supported by an aged translucent rubber outsole.

product.name: Fear of God Athletics x II BASKETBALL 'Ash Pearl'
product.story: The Fear of God Athletics x adidas II BASKETBALL 'Ash Pearl' showcases a muted coral finish on the textile and synthetic suede upper, equipped with interior bootie construction and a molded TPU heel spoiler. The sleek silhouette rests on a partially caged Lightstrike midsole with a TPU shank for midfoot stability. A black bar on the heel displays embossed Fear of God branding.

product.name: Fear of God Athletics x II BASKETBALL High 'Ash Pearl'
product.story: The Fear of God Athletics x adidas II BASKETBALL High 'Ash Pearl' brings together the worlds of basketball and fashion, featuring a mesh upper in a muted pink hue with tonal no-sew synthetic suede overlays. An adjustable ankle strap wraps the high-cut collar for an extra-secure fit. Angular cut-outs on the lateral side panel form the signature three-stripes, while embossed adidas branding adorns the TPU heel spoiler. The high-stop rests on a full-length Lightstrike midsole, partially caged for improved lateral support.

product.name: Little Tokyo Table Tennis x Gel Nimbus 10.1 'Yellow Black'
Wmns SL72 OG 'Black Off White Gum'
Nike Air Max 270 Boston Red Sox
product.story: The MLB x Nike Air Max 270 'City Connect Pack' showcases colors that nod to the Boston Red Sox's alternate uniform inspired by the Green Monster. Built with white engineered mesh, the upper features yellow webbing eyelets and a contrasting green heel counter. The MLB Batterman logo adorns the tongue, while a debossed 'B' graphic graces the back heel. The two-piece midsole combines lightweight Phylon cushioning with a 270-degree Max Air heel unit.
